3.01	Grimoaldo_of_the_Purification	Grimoaldo of the Purification	Blessed Grimoaldo of the Purification, born Ferdinando Santamaria, a religious and clerical student of the Passionist Congregation, born on May 4, 1883 in Pontecorvo, Frosinone, Italy; died November 18, 1902 at Ceccano, Italy. Beatified by Pope John Paul II in 1995.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/45/Grimoaldo.jpg
